You can't do this alone.

627
00:36:11,770 --> 00:36:12,940
我必须去
I have to.

628
00:36:12,970 --> 00:36:14,740
那我跟你去
Then I'm coming with you.

629
00:36:14,770 --> 00:36:15,940
你不能去
You can't.

630
00:36:17,010 --> 00:36:19,980
我被设计来做这些的 约翰
I'm designed to do this, John.

631
00:36:53,620 --> 00:36:55,090
时间到了
It's time.

632
00:36:55,820 --> 00:36:57,750
詹娜
Jenna...

633
00:36:57,790 --> 00:36:59,420
何不能跟我一起来呢
why don't you come with me.

634
00:36:59,460 --> 00:37:01,590
不要 不准碰她
No, no, no. Don't you touch her.

635
00:37:01,630 --> 00:37:03,130
别碰她 把我带走吧
Don't you touch her. Take me!

636
00:37:03,160 --> 00:37:04,900
放她走 不然我干掉你
Let her go! I will shoot you!

637
00:37:04,930 --> 00:37:06,840
不 把我带走吧 不 放开那女孩
No, no! Take me! No, leave her!

638
00:37:06,870 --> 00:37:08,930
把我带走吧 拜托了
Take me! Please! Me!

639
00:37:14,210 --> 00:37:15,480
警察 快趴下
Police! Get down!

640
00:37:37,590 --> 00:37:39,030
你叫什么名字
What's your name?

641
00:37:41,330 --> 00:37:43,910
我从来不杀我不认识的人
I've never killed a man I didn't know.

642
00:37:45,340 --> 00:37:47,310
但是
But then again...

643
00:37:47,340 --> 00:37:49,470
你不是人类
you're not a man.

644
00:37:49,510 --> 00:37:51,090
不是吗
Are you?

645
00:37:53,780 --> 00:37:56,350
你终于出现了 格雷戈
Nice of you to show up, Gregor.

646
00:37:56,390 --> 00:37:57,750
你到底去哪了
Where the hell have you been?

647
00:37:57,790 --> 00:37:59,950
我们以为你挂了
We thought you were dead.

648
00:38:11,630 --> 00:38:12,900
马尔多纳多
Maldonado?

649
00:38:12,930 --> 00:38:14,970
- 约翰 - 人质安全了
- John? - The hostages are secure.

650
00:38:15,000 --> 00:38:16,770
他们是来抢钯的
The whole thing is a palladium heist.

651
00:38:16,800 --> 00:38:17,870
把它关掉 就现在
Shut it off... now!

652
00:38:17,900 --> 00:38:19,930
他们利用我们关闭了整个警报系统
They got us to block the alarm system.

653
00:38:19,970 --> 00:38:21,500
把干扰器关掉
Turn the jammer off!

654
00:38:22,670 --> 00:38:24,770
保罗探员 马上把干扰器关掉
Detective Paul, turn off the jammer now!

655
00:38:24,810 --> 00:38:26,580
关掉它
Shut it off.

656
00:38:37,750 --> 00:38:38,690
走吧
Let's go.

657
00:38:58,140 --> 00:38:59,440
谢啦
Thank you.

658
00:39:06,910 --> 00:39:07,850
约翰
John?

659
00:39:09,490 --> 00:39:10,690
你一定是佩吉
You must be Paige.

660
00:39:18,400 --> 00:39:19,890
谢谢
Thank you.

661
00:39:19,920 --> 00:39:21,560
没呢 谢谢你
No. Thank you.

662
00:39:21,600 --> 00:39:23,100
你很勇敢
You were very brave.

663
00:39:23,140 --> 00:39:25,300
你今天帮忙救了不少人
You helped save a lot of lives today.

664
00:39:26,670 --> 00:39:28,340
你的搭档在哪呢
Where's your partner?

665
00:39:29,380 --> 00:39:31,010
他在...
Oh, he's, uh...

666
00:39:31,040 --> 00:39:32,150
他在进行修补
he's getting patched up.

667
