Jenna, it's a pleasure to meet you.

670
00:39:42,610 --> 00:39:44,180
我听了很多关于你的故事
I've heard a lot about you.

671
00:40:10,980 --> 00:40:12,380
你没事太好啦
I'm glad you're okay.

672
00:40:12,480 --> 00:40:13,950
谢啦
Thanks.

673
00:40:14,280 --> 00:40:16,860
