And I thought you had come down here to thank me.

680
00:40:31,500 --> 00:40:33,200
为什么 因为你履行了你的职责
For what? Doing your job?

681
00:40:33,740 --> 00:40:35,140
申明一下
Just for the record,

682
00:40:35,170 --> 00:40:37,640
我可是提醒过你从那栋楼里出来 对吧
I did tell you to get out of the building, right?

683
00:40:37,680 --> 00:40:40,140
我发誓 我什么也没听到
I swear, all I heard was static.

684
00:40:41,580 --> 00:40:44,710
我要跟你商量个事呢 警探
Oi! I've got a bone to pick with you, Detective.

685
00:40:45,050 --> 00:40:46,490
口香糖 真的假的
Chewing gum? Really?

686
00:40:46,520 --> 00:40:48,490
你能用口香糖修好赛车吗
Would you fix a race car with chewing gum?

687
00:40:48,520 --> 00:40:51,550
是啊 如果它坏了而我还得赢下比赛
Uh, yeah, if it was busted, and I need to win a race.

688
00:40:52,390 --> 00:40:54,390
他需要做个全面检查
He'll need extensive diagnostics.

689
00:40:54,420 --> 00:40:55,920
这个不着急
Ah, that can wait.

690
00:40:55,960 --> 00:40:59,260
来吧 我们去吃面
Come on, let's go get some noodles.

691
00:41:00,300 --> 00:41:01,630
